featured_reviews.review_id:
Probably the most peaceful place in Hyderabad.
I am not supposed to judge prayer places but lemme tell you my experience.
I felt calmness here my mind found peace and the best part was gods beautiful creation the peacock.
There are many in number and the males are huge.
I haven't got the opportunity to see the peacock with its wings open.
I would say to visit this place at least once to witness the serenity.
But a humble request keep the place clean.
There is timing for visiting the park but for mosque there are no timings but don't misuse and try to get in as the park is monitored by CCTV
